descriptionHtml:
---Basic info---
He is a nord
cant be killed
Located around solitude or in the city
---Equipment---
Coin
Imperial sword
Imperial bow
Steel arrows
---Lore---
he was very young when he joined the Empire and when he was 15 the retaking of the imperial city. he saved a solider named Androsos from a burning building. He then went on to Hammerfell to destroy a splinter group that had gotten to far out of hand. It took 2 years to put down the group, he then was relocated to skyrim to deal with the forsworn for 3 to 4 years. After that he was then relocated to Summerset Isles to deal with Thalmor that did not like the treaty signed after the 30 year war. He lost his left eye to a thalomr sniper, After 1 year the splinter group was put down and he stayed in isles for another 5 years. When he left 27 and was relocated to solitude were he resides today.
author: Myth0is
